\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
那么这些基矢量在那些洛伦兹变换下会混合呢？答案就是那些保持
\begin_inset Formula $p^{\mu}$
\end_inset

不变的变换。by definition, little group 的元素。举个例子，在静止系下
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
q^{\mu}=(m,0,0,0)
\]

\end_inset

我们可以选取极化矢量为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\epsilon_{1}^{\mu}(q)=(0,1,0,0),\quad\epsilon_{2}^{\mu}(q)=(0,0,1,0)\quad\epsilon_{3}^{\mu}(q)=(0,0,0,1)
\]

\end_inset

而
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon_{s}^{\mu}=(1,0,0,0)$
\end_inset

