\mathcal{L}=\sqrt{-\det\left(\eta_{\mu\nu}+\frac{1}{M_{\text{P1}}}h_{\mu\nu}\right)}\phi
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $M_{\text{P1}}=G_{N}^{-1/2}\approx\SI{10e19}{\GeV}$
